videos.description: Alabama opens up on the fast break and John Petty unselfishly dishes to Alex Reese for the dunk.
videos.headline: Bama shares on break for dunk

videos.description: Auburn's Bryce Brown misses the wide-open triple, but Jared Harper snatches the rebound and gets the putback bucket.
videos.headline: Harper storms in for putback

videos.description: Collin Sexton creates space with a step back to hit the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Sexton money on step-back 3

videos.description: Collin Sexton is on fire from deep, hitting three consecutive triples in the second half to tie the game 42-42.
videos.headline: Sexton scores 9 straight for Alabama

videos.description: Dazon Ingram pushes the ball in transition, and Galin Smith finishes the blocked layup for the hoop and harm.
videos.headline: Smith finishes dunk for Alabama and-1

videos.description: After trailing by 10 at half, Alabama has taken a 15-point lead after Collin Sexton drains a triple from the wing.
videos.headline: Bama up 15 after another Sexton 3

videos.description: Collin Sexton steals the wild pass and goes behind-the-back to find Donta Hall in transition for the massive dunk.
videos.headline: Sexton's behind-the-back move sets up Hall's slam

videos.description: Collin Sexton scores 31 points on 6-of-8 shooting from deep as Alabama outscores Auburn 50-22 in the second half.
videos.headline: Sexton: 'We're just having fun'
